Python scripts for fetching, parsing, stripping HTML,
splitting content into 160 character chunks,
and posting content into IRC chatrooms.

DEPENDENCIES

% pip install python-irclib
% pip install feedparser


USAGE

originally developed to forward github.com newsfeeds into an IRC room
make a copy of the example config

% cp config.py.example config.py

edit the url with your username and API token 
edit default parameters of the __init__ method in feedcrier.py to change IRC channel(s)

run the script (also join the IRC channel so you can see what happens)

% python feedcrier.py
